<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">submitted his code, the judge gave the verdict &ldquo;TLE&rdquo; (Time Limit Exit). &ldquo;How can I get rid of</div>
